subject: College Athletics
Basketball
lead_paragraph: Tina Charles scored all of her 25 points in the first half and grabbed 13 rebounds to help top-ranked Connecticut rout No. 7 North Carolina, 88-47, on Saturday and win its 54th consecutive game.
